WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:01.573
<i>Previously on Devious Maids...</i>

00:01.609 --> 00:03.433
This picture could destroy
his career.

00:03.468 --> 00:04.801
We need to get him married.

00:04.836 --> 00:05.984
I know just the girl.

00:06.019 --> 00:07.778
I've got to get away
from my family, you know?

00:07.813 --> 00:09.900
It's a group of doctors
who go to third world countries.

00:09.935 --> 00:11.076
He wants me to go with him.

00:11.101 --> 00:12.509
I've written a note.

00:12.544 --> 00:14.742
It explains
why you want her to stay...

00:14.777 --> 00:17.055
and why you needed to leave
without saying good-bye.

00:17.090 --> 00:19.533
I'll bet there's a legal way
to get Miguel in the country.

00:19.568 --> 00:21.386
I get to rescue
the little Mexican boy,

00:21.421 --> 00:22.549
not you.

00:23.074 --> 00:25.209
And to think
you wanted me to wait.

00:25.731 --> 00:26.758
What?

00:27.312 --> 00:30.078
This is where Adrian used to
videotape Flora having sex.

00:30.367 --> 00:32.000
Marisol's real name is Suarez.

00:32.036 --> 00:34.563
She's the mother of the boy
that the police arrested.

00:34.598 --> 00:37.039
This woman...
She's trying to hurt me.

00:37.074 --> 00:38.361
Will I need a gun?

00:40.226 --> 00:42.249
Call 911! Now!

00:47.763 --> 00:48.633
What do we got?

00:48.668 --> 00:49.965
Female, early thirties,

00:50.000 --> 00:52.618
gunshot wound to the abdomen,
B.P. is 80 over 40.

00:52.653 --> 00:55.466
- Pulse?
- 120. Respiratory rate 12.

00:55.501 --> 00:56.671
Bay two. Get moving.

00:56.706 --> 00:58.441
Doctor! Doctor!

00:58.776 --> 01:01.627
I thought you should know my wife.
She's pregnant.

01:01.662 --> 01:03.442
We'll do what we can.

